Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss in the Dark\NEpisode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Kyosuke's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was adopted...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:27.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be down\Nwith a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't have\Na blood relation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:50.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kyosuke-san is still your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:00:59.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:16.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If my lover was Kazu,\Nthen would I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...not had to suffer like now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:32.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But my body doesn't tremble\Nlike the times with Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:36.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because we are not related?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought our relation was something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was born from\Nthe deep and strong bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:51.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...as related family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:54.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this just my own assumption?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frustrating but\Nthey look great together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When are those two going to get\Nmarried?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:26.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become Mizuki Utsunomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we are going to\Nstart the main take!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:44.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kind of aware of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...you and him were doing\Na lot of stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:00.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you keep on getting\Nmore attractive, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:06.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...when we were changing for gym class,\NI saw some love marks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But because you guys are family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:16.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had underrated saying\Nnothing was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:25.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since today I found out you guys\Nwere not related, I made my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:31.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I nominate myself! To become your lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:32.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We are childhood friends\Nand close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't in a relationship to\Ndo something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:50.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say not right now,\Nthen when is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:56.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited this long...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting is hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:37.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:56.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are sleeping in a place\Nlike this, you will catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was okay if you were\Nin bed ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty late today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:11.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After work, I was seeing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:22.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I worried about this alone and\Nyou're on a date with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with Kazu too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to make things clear now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the family registry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about the copy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, I submitted it the\Nday of the enrollment ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't talk and ask questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:08.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you would be worried\Nthinking who your real parent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what concerns me the most is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am l...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being left alone at home\Nmade you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I wasn't lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:52.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why is this little boy crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came home and\Nyou are so passionate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you asking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:19.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I am not going to be okay\Nif you are not with me, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So wasteful to abandon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke, Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this is\Njust a normal "love"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:47.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the fact if I'm related\Nor not related to him, I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...Love with Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Kyosuke, once again\NI am this bright and lively this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:08.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:13.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Papa-san is going to\Nget married with Mizuki Utsunomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:13.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, recently everyone is\Ntalking about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:21.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\NI saw them at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two had this out of\Nthe ordinary ambience...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Their marriage is just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that true? I thought it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:31.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's most likely\Nmy misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,More than that, it's about\Nyesterday's answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about that, you don't\Nhave to tell me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kazu, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:09:00.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, my mom has gone\Ntotally crazy for Kyosuke-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, at the parents get-together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that the\Nparents get-together was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said the scenery from\Nthe hotel was beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was your mom there with Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting angry for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The hall for the parents get-together\Nwas the hotel in bayside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:30.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or better yet, if our parents get\Ntogether, then we'll be brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...if your papa and\Nmy mom get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can live together without\Nbeing bothered by anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:46.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Having nice parents and\Na sibling who get along...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:53.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought for a little that\NI wish something like that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lost kitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Utsunomiya senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it seem like you can\Nblend in with the new class?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:13.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, I'm in the same class\Nas my childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is my\Nchildhood friend Kazuki Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:28.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu, this is Utsunomiya senpai.\NHe's the student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mira, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come visit the student\Ncouncil room whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? It's so not you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go near him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:03.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me at the enrollment\Nceremony and he's a nice good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot? Idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot? Idiot?\NHe looks at you like he wants to eat you\Nup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks at you like he wants to eat you\Nup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha? I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good at acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...the son of the great\Nactress Mizuki Utsunomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:22.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:51.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because he's the son of an\Nactress doesn't make him good at acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way he looked at you...\NHis ulterior motives were totally clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:56.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious! Because I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:12.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:23.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You will seriously become a great wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:29.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right? Good cook and good in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher is calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:38.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke-san was in an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you wouldn't\Nleave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die with Kyosuke too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you shake him that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you shake him that much...\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:27.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...\NIt's okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:28.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke!\NIt's okay, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be quieter in a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you are\Nworried about me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:47.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully it was only a light injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...so he will be able to\Nget out in 2 to 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hojo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let Kyosuke rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:24.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he didn't use a stunt man\Nsince it wasn't that dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently there was\Nsome kind of miscommunication...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke should take advantage\Nof this time and take a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him until late last night\Nthat he's been working too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then last night Kyosuke was late\Nbecause he was with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...the president of the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I totally thought\Nhe was on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:52.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He pretends like he is\Nhorsing around all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:57.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:02.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are fooled by it, then no wonder\Neveryone else gets fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretending to be a playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been an honest man\Nsince back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:10.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy. Even his beloved Mira\Nhas misunderstood him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to convince him\Nmany times that it's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...to raise you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he would raise you\Nand wouldn't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:31.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I need to take my hat off for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:36.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are really important to Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to take care of him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you grew up\Nto be a very good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:52.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He always talks about how\Nyou are so cute and brags about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Brags about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does he know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:05.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Kyosuke took me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:22.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, if I didn't sprain\Nmy ankle, he wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault...\NKyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:29.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He never told me that him and Mizuki\NUtsunomiya were costarring together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's calling\NKyosuke with familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you by any chance Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:44.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...actress's tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:05.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Mr. Kyosuke Munakata\Nwas released from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a rumor that he got hurt\Nin place of Ms. Mizuki Utsunomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's been said\Nthat their marriage is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, all the channels are\Ntalking about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask what business you have with\Nme?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to become my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:17.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's not possible!\NMeaning she wants to marry Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:20.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning she wants to marry Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father won't allow you to do that.\NMeaning she wants to marry Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My father won't allow you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he said if you are okay\Nwith it, he doesn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have the right to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she say that\Nshe has the right to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...with that much confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:56.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke didn't really\Nagree to marry her, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, that cloud looks like a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:21.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa likes that one next to it that\Nlooks like a soft serve ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to take a boat and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...go to another county\Nfar away together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa wants to eat a plum\Nflavored soft serve ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...tired now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is... I looked around for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I went everywhere that you might go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:42.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what I was\Ngoing to do if you were gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to cry\Nif it was a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:21:01.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I disappear, there are\Nmany people who will love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anybody\Nwho will replace you, Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:12.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason for me\Nto live in this world is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, that woman came to our home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mizuki Utsunomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:28.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:35.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she came all the way\Nto our home and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...asked if I wanted\Nto become her son...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...saying that she has the right to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made her go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:22:00.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think about your happiness,\NI don't have the right to do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:05.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. I should have talked\Nto you about this a lot earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:06.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:09.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of your birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:13.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:17.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something was\Nwrong from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki Utsunomiya is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:26.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:29.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You just said you knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:34.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about how she is my older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:35.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:42.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki and l... We lost our parents\Nwhen we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived just the two of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:50.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We used our beauty in a useful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:55.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even without parents,\Nwe were living like pretty well off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when Mizuki was about to be\Nthe star of the celebrity world...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...she became pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She made a decision to have\Nthe child and raise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:13.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when an offer from Hollywood\Nfor her to star in a film came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that,\Nmyself who was in High school...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:20.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...took you in to raise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:25.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So she grabbed the Hollywood dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:29.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange,\NI raised an adorable baby and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...ate him all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:35.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say it,\Nit doesn't become a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:41.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if she is my mother, then\Nwhat about Utsunomiya senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:43.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.97,0:23:44.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:50.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takayuki is the son of the movie\Ndirector that Mizuki married afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:55.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the father has\Npassed away a couple of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:58.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:03.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's not that Kyosuke and I don't\Nhave any kind of blood relation at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy and troubled...\NIt's a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:12.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kyosuke, you worked\Nreally hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:14.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.14,0:24:17.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am going repay you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:20.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you become senile,\NI'll change your diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:22.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even give you a\Npiggyback, and huggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:24.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you to do it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you to do it right now?\NYou're heavy! I'll be squashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:27.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy! I'll be squashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.58,0:24:30.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:35.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...am I allowed to stay\Nby you now on too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.52,0:24:36.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.29,0:24:40.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get you to\Nrepay what you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.47,0:24:45.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.97,0:24:47.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cherish me for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:48.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:51.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's right this second...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.59,0:25:10.15,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,As much for me to forget to blink...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:13.89,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm occupied with\Njust you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.06,0:25:21.26,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop the time forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.20,0:25:27.57,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,This room that no one's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.41,0:25:35.18,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The TV is vacant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.69,0:25:42.15,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I look for a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:49.49,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I pretend I wasn 't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.56,0:25:54.40,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong? We most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.50,0:25:57.96,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,...don 't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:26:08.07,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Because not even\None person knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.32,0:26:11.95,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,As much for me to forget to blink...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:15.61,E-ED,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm occupied with\Njust you all the time.
